### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Home Route
GET http://localhost:5000/

### Register User (Real Gmail - Email Test)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zaheen Ahmad",
  "email": "finaltest@ethereal.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Register User (Fake Email - for testing without email)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@shopzone.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@shopzone.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Create Payment Order
POST http://localhost:5000/api/payments/create-order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 500
}

### Verify Payment (after getting order details)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/payments/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "order_xxxx",
  "paymentId": "pay_xxxx",
  "signature": "xxxx"
}

### Get Product Reviews
GET http://localhost:5000/api/reviews/product/PRODUCT_ID

### Add Product Review (Need Token)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "productId": "PRODUCT_ID",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excellent product! Highly recommended."
}

### Get Wishlist
GET http://localhost:5000/api/wishlist
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Add to Wishlist
POST http://localhost:5000/api/wishlist/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "productId": "PRODUCT_ID"
}

### Validate Coupon
POST http://localhost:5000/api/coupons/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "WELCOME10",
  "cartTotal": 2999
}

### Admin Dashboard Stats (Need Admin Token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Users (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Products (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/products
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Coupons (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/coupons
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Reviews (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/reviews
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE